channel.title: Looking for help possibly a team
channel.description:
Hello, so i have done a basic private server yearssss ago and have lost the touch i guess.. I am looking for some help I guess im going to try to make a successful private server but no clue where to start on the JDK (i have 1.6.0_24 and 1.6.0_02) also the source i have Pimpscape but every time i go to compile it gives me the following
:::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::: :::::::::: :: :: :: Please wait while Afterlife's Server is Compiled.. :: :: :: :::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::: ::::::::::
Note: stream.java uses or overrides a deprecated API. Note: Recompile with -Xlint:deprecation for details.
:::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::: :::::::::: :: :: :: Afterlife's Server has been compiled successfully! :: :: :: :::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::: ::::::::::
Press any key to continue . . .
Any ideas on why? I am willing to change anything and everything or even if i could get a team going on a private server of people who know more than me would be great and could even possibly go for a 614+ client. I would also love to get a custom client going but i know that wont happen and that is fine with me. Not trying to get "gimme gimme" "free server made" or anything like that just looking for help and tips. Thank you to all!
